channel.title: Comments on: SELLOUT: Joe Jackson loans “One More Time” to Cheesy Gordita factory

item.title: By: Matt Schwimmer
item.dc:creator: Matt Schwimmer
item.description: Actually, fuck the Gordita, Joe Jackson's new album Rain is mind-blowingly amazing. Check it out, and forever ditch the Taco Bell.
